  "instructions": [
    "Heat the melted butter in a large saucepan over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the chicken breast pieces and cook until browned",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, and salt, and stir to combine",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir to combine",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes",
    "Stir in the orange blossom water",
    "Serve in a stone bowl"
